<br>
No level 40 warrior waltzes into Sebilis and complains that he can't keep aggro on the red con mobs, but when the same warrior reaches his 50s and tries his hand at ToV, suddenly it's a big design flaw and warriors are broken? Level up on appropriate content and come back when you're 60. Get appropriate taunting weapons, and have the guild give you a 5 second head start. It works wonders.<br>
<br>
